projects: [{'title': 'From Vocational Training to Success', 'date': {'start': {'month': 8, 'day': None, 'year': 2012}, 'end': {'month': 7, 'day': None, 'year': 2014}}, 'description': 'The project "From Vocational Training to Success" will connect European countries Croatia, the Netherlands and Slovenia in the field of VET within the field of entrepreneurship in tourism. Through visits, participants will exchange training experiences, study materials, learn more about each other VET field and also improve the VET system in the future. They will also visit different enterprises and institutions to collect good practice examples and to study different approaches and ways in entrepreneurship. Meetings between participating institutions will be organized on regular basis by partners in their countries. On these meetings, participants will compare collected good practice examples and discuss on different methods used in entrepreneurship training. The project result will be a built partnership network between participants and Guidelines for VET containing good practice examples and specific modules for training in entrepreneurship. Guidelines will be available on DVD, as a printed edition and online, and can be used in every institution. The project will bridge the gap between vocational education and the labour market since the participants involved in the project are representatives of the labour market and institutions that provide vocational training. This European partnership will also increase the participants qualifications, professional competence and experiences in the field of VET. These new gained professional competence will be used, by the participants, in the professional training and education of their trainees. The project will have impact on the improvement of training process in the participating organizations, and a broader impact on bringing the project results to all European organizations.less', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Linda Andrea', 'last_name': 'Fijma', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Owner Capmo'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Jurgen', 'last_name': '✍ Hillaert', 'name': None, 'headline': 'De Streekverkenner - ziet de verbanden.
